##Diary of the outbreak | the eighth day of the siege of Wuhan

Plantifulsoul

Introduction to behindmylife

2020.1.30

The Eighth Day, stay at home too long, time seems to stand still, do not check the phone is not sure what day today, for the first time feel long holiday. The Sixth Day, the original tomorrow on the official work, the project issued a notice postponed to the tenth day, Wuhan to the Lantern Festival are not necessarily let go.

The weather is very good, the wind is warm, the hand out completely not cold, in a few days is the beginning of spring, Spring 2020 came a little early, do not come what pour cold, direct into summer I can accept.

The temperature just rose, can not bear the boring daily Wuhan people have taken to the streets, we do not drive, walk, take a cloth bag ride a small blue car to buy vegetables. There are people who don't wear masks, and if the look in their eyes kills bacteria, I'm afraid my glare has already disinfected them hundreds of times.

Whether it's a lockdown on the way home, or a laptop that gets flooded and breaks down, emotions now resemble the five stages of grief: denial, anger, negotiation, negativity, and acceptance. I've been angry, I've cried, I've broken down, and now I'm at peace with it. Yesterday, my classmates gave me the link to the free online psychological consultation during the epidemic. I said, how did you know I needed it? But I was still too late. I had already arranged for psychological intervention the day before yesterday. I had been treated online several times, and it felt OK. In fact, through the screen, doctors don't jump to conclusions. I let off steam as a listener.

I thought I had cried enough and could not squeeze out tears. Yesterday, when I saw the experience of writing about Qian Qian Qian in public on earth, I could not help bursting into tears when I saw half of it. I felt that too strong empathy was also not a good thing. Tiny emotions were magnified dozens of times, i may only know a tenth of Qianqian's grief, so I am sad. In the story of these people, I was always a bystander, but still in between the lines experienced a loss of loved ones grief, as if a foot into the abyss, falling again and again, but always unable to land.

The computer that types now is bought eight years ago, the floor of the study is covered with Ash, special card, type A word card for three seconds, type A word card for one minute, heat dissipation is also poor, broadcast the video is hot can carry hand, really don't know how to insist on playing online games with it before. This was put in the computer just broken, I am afraid of the gas can put the keyboard out of the hole, now slowly hit Bai, a word of a word of the knock, at home idle is idle.

Retired every day, still regular sleep, at 10:00,5:30 wake up, but there is no heat at home, always stay in bed for half an hour before getting up, "take off clothes need to do psychological building ahead of time. ".

I like to look at people, or observe them, and watch them in silence. Everyone is busy with their own affairs. It's interesting to see the self as a ghost pulled away. On Weibo, I saw a suggestion that Wuhan residents write their own stories in a booklet. I agreed that the lives of ordinary people need to be recorded, seen and understood.

Many people are concerned about whether the supplies are still in short supply, yes, medical supplies are not enough, the number of infected people is too large, the numbers continue to grow, protective equipment needs to be replaced in time, hospitals in Wuhan are not enough, and the surrounding cities are even more in short supply, ordinary pharmacies can not buy masks and disinfectants, all out of stock, the way to find my uncle to borrow masks, said to run several pharmacies can not buy, I go out unarmed, can not help.

Supplies are also tight, and vegetables are hard to get. Basically, there are only turnips, cabbage and potatoes. But in winter, cabbage and radish are also delicious, tender and sweet. There are also specialties from Hubei, such as the Artemisia Sphaerocephala and Lotus rhizome. Pork is almost extinct, beef and chicken are the only things you can see in the nearby supermarket, and people ask each day when there will be pork. No initial rush of crazy appearance, slowly pushing the cart, in front of the purchase list one by one to buy, pay the queue orderly, are gradually accustomed to life after the city.

There were a lot of walkers and joggers in the park near my home, an old man sunning himself on a bench, and a man fishing in a hat by the lake. I wondered if he could actually catch a fish, and I got a closer look. The Sun was too comfortable, the man lay down on the rock and fell asleep.

Chimonanthus Praecox was in full bloom, the cream colored flowers and bones, an old couple went to the tree to take a photo, the old man and the old woman were wearing masks, or said cheerfully, "good smell, " as soon as they said that I really smelled plum blossom fragrance, a few puffs from far away through the mask, actually can not smell what flavor, still nod toward them.

There are also many orange trees in the park, hung with fist-sized Tangerines, heavy clusters of them, to lure passers-by to pick them, the lower ones have long been picked, the higher ones can only stare, I am hesitant to jump up to pick a few fruits, an old man with a bamboo pole I do not know where to find, extended pole down four or five, may see me standing on the side of the embarrassed, asked me to take one home to taste, I said it's okay, you take it all.

When he was tired of walking, he stood by the lake and rested. Among the reeds were waterbirds. At first he thought they were wild ducks until he saw them get up and show their long, thin legs. The water was shimmering in the sun, there was no wind in the afternoon, and I couldn't see the sparkling waves. Facing the still surface of the lake, I suddenly felt like the Lady of "Calm Leisure" who gave me a bicycle and an Afro, the next second, we're in the shot.

Every day adhere to feed the community of stray cats, these days seems and I cooked a bit, a few orange cat heard me shout "Kitty" , automatically rub up against my trouser legs, meow Sajiao. Cow Cat and civet cat or high cold, squinting at me, just close to run away with Tail Upright. I still hope to contact the volunteers when I have the chance. I can sterilize the cats in the community. It is not a good way to give birth to a litter.

Shopping, walking, riding a bike, feeding the cat, reading, watching TV... Last night with colleagues, this kind of life too long, waiting to go back to work, I am afraid that serious business forgotten, clearly early retirement is still very early, but early experience unemployed life.

I still have anger inside me, and being angry and alert is one of the ways I fight. Every day, I see new messages asking for help on Weibo, many of them are family group infections, there is no place for hospitals, the community doesn't care, and I have to prove my identity in desperation, that means it's not a lie. I watched them get so sick that, in addition to retweeting and retweeting, my The Hours burned with my own powerlessness. For some families, the outbreak is simply keeping them indoors. For others, it could be a death blow. These days the sun, bask in the heat of the time, I will tell myself cherish the warmth of the moment, the accumulation of grief is too much, about to pour out, have to open their hearts, bask in.

Unfortunately, there is also, I miss my cat very much, according to the plan, my fifth day ticket back to Xi'an, I should have picked him up yesterday, but unfortunately a bout of pneumonia, he was forced to stay in the hospital, to see the video sent by the doctor, it was obvious that he was anxious and shouted, toys don't help. Siam is lively and mischievous, more active than the general cat, stay in the cage occasionally out of the yard completely can not meet his needs, although I often complain that he loves to break up the family, jump up and down, at this time and feel sorry for him, but hope that he can scratch the sofa, play with the curtains.

This morning, I changed my wechat profile picture to a couple kissing through a gas mask. When I saw the bandits, I also started to write a diary about the closure of the city. In extraordinary times, I suggest you to write about "love during the period of pneumonia" and write about the "love of the closure of the city" , which originated from real life, maybe we can come up with a couple of white tassels and Fan Liuyuan.

Finally, here are a few new shows to enjoy at home:
1. The Japanese dramas ship of theseus and 10 secrets, suspense plot, what you don't need to know, and see them and you'll understand, plot;
2. American drama "The Stranger" , suspense thriller;
3. South Korean drama "Black Dog" , workplace drama;
4. The future of fashion, a fashion show hosted by Miss Chung and Tan from Queer Five.

In the diary of my thoughts, "I was in bad shape for a while, so I found a teacher to learn Chinese painting. The class was held in Tanhualin, near the Hubei Academy of Fine Arts, a bit like the Nanluoguxiang of Beijing... crab got out of his car and walked up the uphill path, zigzagging, quieter and quieter, until he saw Tanhualin's densely packed pear blossom, as if spring were in full bloom." Tanhualin is now being developed into a small business circle, with an especially large number of young tourists, crowds of people moving around during the holidays, and it is difficult to move in the alleys. Countless human fireworks have been added to the small and fresh paths of literature and art that we have been taking. Recently, when we went there, they are old people who are waiting in line to buy food. It would be "full of vitality" to have a few loud words of Wuhan dialect.
